description: Keep believing and the dream that you wish will come TRUE as our Disney princess learns in our sparkling “Adorable Cinderella” puzzle! Bippity, boppity, boo! Assemble 100 glittering pieces to reveal beautiful Cinderella, ready for the ball, attended by her fairy godmother, the coachman, and her many mice friends. Best of all, every single piece in this puzzle is unique - no duplicates. Jigsaw puzzles help support a child's development as they play, building skills such as concentration and creativity. They also make for great storytelling and family together time when parents puzzle with their children. Start connecting!
